Leah and Keisha have been best friends for forever. They see each other almost every day and share all their intimate secrets. Leah has been dating Jean for a while now, and her ultimate fantasy is to share him with the one girl who means everything to her. On a hot sunny day by the pool, sexual chemistry is in the air, and Leah encourages Jean to kiss Keisha in the cool water. One thing leads to another and once they are in the house, still hot and wet, they embark on a sexual experience the three of them will be bonded with forever. From now on, its not just secrets these two beauties will share
